{"tid":2223058,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"長沙灣大慶燒味半年內七度被定罪　扣滿55分遭食環署取消牌照","createTime":"2020-09-29T13:50:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-07T07:37:58.000Z","uid":244704,"like":28,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"092b5b0470a917aedc37e3970ae55a3922426079","tid":2223058,"uid":244704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T13:50:43.000Z","msg":"　　位於長沙灣青山道242號鋪地下的大慶燒味飯店，因沒有妥善貯存未加掩蓋的食物、在露天地方配製食物、食物室不潔、容受處所內有蟑螂及老鼠，屢次違反《食物業規例》，今日（29日）被食環署取消牌照。<br />\n<br />\n　　食環署今日（29日）公布，位於深水埗青山道242號鋪地下、名為「大慶」的食肆，因沒有妥善貯存未加掩蓋的食物、在露天地方配製食物、食物室不潔、容受處所內有蟑螂及老鼠，屢次違反《食物業規例》。去年4月至9月期間，該餐廳7次被法庭定罪，共罰款10,300元，食環署亦根據違例記分制記下持牌人55分，食肆因此被取消牌照。<br />\n<br />\n　　發言人提醒食物業處所持牌人必須遵守《食物業規例》，否則牌照可能被暫時吊銷或取消。<br />\n<br />\n　　食環署指，持牌食物業處所須在處所入口附近顯眼處展示已領有牌照的告示，以資識別。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202009/29/P2020092900373.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F202009%2F29%2FP2020092900373.htm&d=uIqzu4H250jM%2FFVIgxmQWNEgU5aikFnqk5iyu2dsMw0%3D&h=be4033a8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202009/29/P2020092900373.htm</a>"},{"pid":"75802cd8e37cd4ad6d40b63c9365f670827a9579","tid":2223058,"uid":87511,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T13:52:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hkchronicles.com/data/19aead2c6aa1dbb5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkchronicles.com%2Fdata%2F19aead2c6aa1dbb5&d=uIqzu4H250jM%2FFVIgxmQWNEgU5aikFnqk5iyu2dsMw0%3D&h=35659446\" target=\"_blank\">https://hkchronicles.com/data/19aead2c6aa1dbb5</a><br />\n<br />\n弓起弓起"},{"pid":"88a5dd55fa4f6389b01c92db3750f183a697ac72","tid":2223058,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"75802cd8e37cd4ad6d40b63c9365f670827a9579","tid":2223058,"uid":87511,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T13:52:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hkchronicles.com/data/19aead2c6aa1dbb5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.c